      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   opn-seq-out-000      thru opn-seq-out-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se errori                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        g-sts                =    e-not-err
                     go to exe-exp-ofv-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
